title: DAZ3D - Poser - Nano Suit War Pack (DAZ 13463) EXE
description:
This requires the Nano Suit for Genesis base.

Nano Suit War Pack is a great add-on for the Genesis Nano Suit that comes in two styles: Marine and DD. Create the classic battle between Good and Evil.

The materials look war torn and include various symbols. There are also camouflage sets for jungle and desert environments. The materials come with custom diffuse secular and bump maps all in 4096x4096 to give you outstanding quality.

It has a great range of colors and a huge shader set, so you can mix-and-match to create your own styles. They also work great with the existing shader sets, including matching sets for the gun. So let the Future Wars begin.
